    Replace all emoji/unicode icons with Lucide React components (Task #16)
    
    - Replaced ~223+ emoji and unicode character icons across App.js with
      Lucide React components (X, Check, ChevronDown, ChevronRight, ChevronUp,
      Mail, Scale, Calendar, CheckSquare, etc.)
