      to store Lucide component references instead of emoji strings
    - Updated Accordion component and all icon rendering code to render
      component references directly (removed broken typeof checks)
    - Added new Lucide imports: Sun, Moon, Paperclip, Circle, Phone, Printer
    - Replaced ✕/× close buttons with <X />, ▸/▾/▶/▼ toggles with
      ChevronRight/ChevronDown/ChevronUp, ● dots with Circle, ✓ checkmarks
      with Check, ✎ edit with Pencil, 🔁 recurring with RefreshCw,
      ↻ retry with RotateCcw, ⇅ sort with ChevronDown
    - Zero emoji characters remain in the codebase
    - Updated replit.md to document icon architecture

